Key Match Events: Rassie van der Dussen scored 133 runs off 118 balls, achieving a strike rate of 112.71
Quinton de Kock scored 114 runs off 116 balls, contributing significantly to South Africa's total

Post-Match Reflections: Rassie van der Dussen was named Player of the Match for his outstanding performance

Miscellaneous Highlights: South Africa won by 190 runs, securing a comprehensive victory

Quinton de Kock was dismissed by Mitchell, while Daryl Mitchell was also dismissed by Rabada
